2.  **[ ]** Initialize a Docker `base-forge` image with Node.js/Python pre-installed for sandboxing.
3.  **[ ]** Define the `PolicySchema` used by the Persona Switchboard.
4.  **[ ]** Implement the `WeightedScheduler` loop in the main AGI Heartbeat.
